Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:42.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}誰かが差し伸べた手を　振り解いて進む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:48.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}「自由な不自由」蔓延る場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}何かに追われるように　生き急ぐ毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:59.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}信じ続けた真実も　わからなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:04.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}何が本当の幸せなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:10.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}その答えを知る者など　此処には居ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Where is my god?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:16.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}荒れ果てた夢が　眠る大地で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:21.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}死んだように生きるなんて　僕には出来なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:27.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}生まれ変われ　今　光を秘めし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}最後の希望　そして奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:38.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}もう一度世界に　輝きを放て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:42.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}掙脫一切援助之手前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:48.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}在身陷充滿禁錮的自由之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.15,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}似乎每天都被什麼追趕  度日匆匆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:59.23,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}連一直深信不疑的真相  亦不明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:04.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}到底什麼才是真正的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:10.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}這裡無人知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:16.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}在荒廢的夢想沉睡的大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:21.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我無法如活死人般地生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:27.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}當下轉世重生  蘊藏光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}讓最後的希望和奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:38.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}在世界上再一次綻放光輝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:56.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}終わらないメロディーを歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:04.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:12.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:21.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:26.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:31.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:37.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:49.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:55.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:59.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:03.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:07.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:13.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:27.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠と　儚さと　震える夜もあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:56.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}歌唱無盡的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:04.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}儘管愛不忍釋  心有淒楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:12.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}仍因為無法遏制而厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:21.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即使我就在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:31.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}映入眼簾的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:37.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}不盡相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:49.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}心意  未來  笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:55.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}對  還有未知的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}心已知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:27.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永恆  短暫  與顫抖的夜晚並存
